{"tid":1290782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[7.7遊行] 西九高鐡站野餐後自由活動 注意事項","createTime":"2019-07-06T15:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T05:27:44.000Z","uid":231040,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"627a609c41d35d86a1d1be5705a0ef66a99c9cff","tid":1290782,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:24:38.000Z","msg":"相信今日大家遊行到西九高鐡站後一定會&quot;意猶未盡&quot;,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 加上&quot;<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">天口㷫㷫地</span></strong>&quot;</span>, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定會好想<span style=\"color: pink;\">瘋狂地參觀吓呢個</span><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">駛咗我地成900億</span></strong>兼<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">割咗忽地俾中共</span></strong>嘅&quot;<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">喪權辱港</span></strong></span>&quot;車站, 順便涼吓冷氣, 同埋&quot;<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同鄰國嘅朋友瘋狂聯誼</span></span>&quot;一吓</span>....<br />\n<br />\n為咗可以令大家&quot;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">盡㷫而歸</span></strong></span>&quot;, 而家有一啲嘅事項要同大家講吓 -<br />\n1) 犬群已經表示, 西九高鐡站將會有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>大約一千隻犬駐守</ins></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />;<br />\n2) 根據昨日嘅觀察, 有大量犬隻嘅車輛全日不停進出西九龍站落客區及附近一帶道路, 加上今日車站嘅停車場已經出咗通告會於下午間歇性封閉, 所以預計西九高鐡站嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><ins>B1出境大堂</ins></span></span></strong>會係成個犬群嘅&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>核心保護區域</ins></span></strong></span>&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 而<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">車站嘅B1上落客區</span></strong></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">B2停車場</span></strong></span>會係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">犬群嘅集散區域</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HcXJ8D1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHcXJ8D1.jpg&h=2bca4532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gb0jGY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGb0jGY4.jpg&h=1a27c837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 相比起香港區, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">尖沙咀嘅地形對於自由活動人士較為不利</span></strong></span>, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>易攻難守</strong></span>&quot;,<span style=\"color: pink;\"> 要包抄亦相對容易</span></span>, 所以, <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>請大家務必緊記一定要集體行動及離開</ins></span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">並且熟知以下嘅路線圖</span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以免離開時容易&quot;被狗咬&quot;</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7S6mZe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7S6mZe.jpg&h=d8eb7766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZVWKcA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZVWKcA.jpg&h=975a51b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGtQOEg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGtQOEg.jpg&h=1181d7f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">希望大家野餐玩得開開心心, 齊齊冇穿冇爛咁回家!!!~~~ </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e05ffe41ea0ba93c4d94d5e7d3fc2fe1baf21cc3","tid":1290782,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"巴打你好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e5b11b53799f06fdf4a725fadc2e556ea95b37","tid":1290782,"uid":258703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4ceb370aef05ca822ed0b2d2f086f219bed80f","tid":1290782,"uid":176442,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"彌敦道食放題？"},{"pid":"d700134f3a2afa3d14aee9e0cc24e29f4889ca68","tid":1290782,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10159f8e64bee832ca2eb2fbfc0831ceea90e46f","tid":1290782,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:34:30.000Z","msg":"入出境大堂等車犯唔犯法？"},{"pid":"9ba646327441daef0bda4b4fe555a15b365805cf","tid":1290782,"uid":258788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"手足我地要小心，同時要友善！ we are facing the world!"},{"pid":"e5fe53a7cfdc7d50499dfcae5dbcddca83768084","tid":1290782,"uid":106286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5P0S2aQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht